commit.message: Add sdist to release process notes
Remove old Django versions from tox config
Update manifest to include test suite

Move help_text to form field

Default help_text values are non-standard, and it should probably be
removed. However, moving this to the form field allows subclasses to
override or otherwise disable this.
Add bound vs unbound rendering tests
Move forms tests to separate module

Fix form field styling

Readds indentation and adds spaces after separators

Fix form field kwargs handling

Ensure dump/load kwargs are provided to the init method instead of
setting them on the instance after initialization.
